One person died and three others were injured following a bizarre shooting inside a Parliament Street, Central bar at about 2am on Wednesday. It is not clear at this stage what happened but it is believed gangsters were involved. Within an hour, the body of one of the alleged gunmen was found lying next to the getaway car in Stanford Road, Bethelsdorp. Police spokeswoman Colonel Priscilla Naidu said a statement would be released later on Wednesday. Members of the gang intervention unit are investigating. Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share